latestIgtvVideos.title: Different Ways To Style A Puff Sleeve Ruffle Top💖
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I have styled this stunning puff sleeve fluorescent pink ruffle top in 5 different ways! ❤️
Look1: The volume of this top is amazing so I made it into a crop top and styled it with a plain black side slit skirt with a nice pair of black furry heels .🖤
Look2:  As you must have seen in my previous videos I really like experimenting with my clothes. I wore the blouse on one sleeve and tucked the other half inside the top and styled the left over strings over the neck and shoulder area giving the top an absolutely different look and paired it with a pair of middle slit pants accessorising it with a pair of earrings and sunglasses. 🧡
Look3: For this look I decided to go for a 
colour-block look . I styled my orange Jumpsuit with this fluorescent pink ruffle top with a pair of sleek sunglasses and tan loafers.🧡
Look4: For this look I styled the same Jumpsuit in a different way just to show that there are plenty of ways one can style these pieces together.
Look5. This can be too bright for some people but I still went ahead and styled this look. I decided to go for a monochromatic look for this one . I styled a fluorescent pink pants with this top and added a rhinestone embellished belt to balance the details of the outfit . 💖
I Hope you guys enjoy watching the video as much as I enjoyed filming it.🥰

latestIgtvVideos.title: 🤩 Raksha Bandhan Outfit Ideas🤩
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
This Raksha Bandhan notch up your style.😍
Look 1: Chanderi Suit set with Kundan and pearl necklace and mojari.❤️
Look 2 : I wore a white gharara with pastel blue kurti and teamed it up with some chunky silver earrings. #gottapatti 💓
Look 3: I Wore a lehriya kurti with a gharara, You can also wear it with a nice pair of white cigarette pants or a palazzo . To pop the outfit a little bit more I went ahead and added a piece of Kundan choker to make the outfit stand out a little more . 🥰
Look 4: I love wearing traditional jewellery with western outfits . This is more of an experimental look . I wore a stain black shirt with some ripped denim jeans and accessorised it with some traditional jewellery and mojari. 
Look 5: This one is from my own label @yaminimehradesigns ! I wore a pastel lemon yellow short Kurti with gharara 
and styled it with a golden sling bag and mojari.💛
